$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
id_adjective

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
id_adjective -  This method is similar to the id function, except this will check the adjectives instead of the aliases and the name.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int id_adjective(string word)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the word to check
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the word matches one of the adjectives, 0 otherwise
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/id.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is similar to the id function, except this will check the
adjectives instead of the aliases and the name.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
id(), id_plural()

.EP

